# 📺 githubvideopodcast
### Turn Any GitHub Repository Into a Full Video Podcast Automatically

githubvideopodcast converts any GitHub repo into a complete **video podcast episode** — script, narration, subtitles, and final MP4 — all generated with a single command.

It transforms your README, docs, or code notes into a narrated, captioned, social‑ready video for YouTube, TikTok, Instagram, LinkedIn, or your own site.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Repo extraction — pulls README.md or any file directly from GitHub  
- AI voiceover — generates natural narration using high‑quality TTS  
- Auto subtitles — creates SRT captions synced to the script  
- Video rendering — builds a kinetic‑text video with background + styling  
- One‑command output — produces a final MP4 ready to publish  
- Fully local — no API keys required  
- Unlimited usage — generate as many videos as you want  

